{"tid":694626,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年金球獎集中討論區","createTime":"2018-06-08T13:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T08:44:24.000Z","uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d743765c2062dd2bdaa5af5f96a499a88da0f6ac","tid":694626,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"今年估計都係美斯同C朗之爭，但係今年兩個鬥得好緊。先分析一下過去十年兩人得到金球獎的勝出原因。<br />\n<br />\n2008<br />\nc朗勝<br />\nc朗帶領曼聯贏出歐聯。<br />\n美斯當時未成為隊內核心。<br />\n<br />\n2009<br />\n美斯勝<br />\n美斯帶領巴塞自然年六冠王。<br />\nC朗四大皆空。<br />\n<br />\n2010<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯勝(無歐聯)</span><br />\n美斯只有聯賽冠軍。<br />\nC朗四大皆空。<br />\n<br />\n2011<br />\n美斯勝<br />\n美斯聯賽、歐聯雙冠，自然年五冠(僅失國王盃)。<br />\nC朗只有國王盃。<br />\n<br />\n2012<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美斯勝(無歐聯)</span><br />\n美斯只有國王盃。<br />\nC朗只有聯賽冠軍。<br />\n*皇馬巴塞均止步於歐聯四強<br />\n<br />\n2013<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">C朗勝(無歐聯)</span><br />\n美斯只有聯賽冠軍。<br />\nc朗四大皆空。<br />\n*皇馬巴塞均止步於歐聯四強<br />\n<br />\n2014<br />\nC朗勝<br />\n美斯四大皆空。<br />\nC朗歐聯和國王盃冠軍，自然年四冠。<br />\n<br />\n2015<br />\n美斯勝<br />\n美斯歐洲三冠王，自然年五冠(僅失國內超級盃)。<br />\nC朗四大皆空。<br />\n<br />\n2016<br />\nC朗勝<br />\n美斯國內雙冠。<br />\nC朗歐聯冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n2017<br />\nC朗勝<br />\n美斯僅得國王盃。<br />\nC朗獲聯賽冠軍和歐聯冠軍，自然年五冠(僅失國王盃)<br />\n<br />\n憑記憶可能有錯。"},{"pid":"dbcbdedb8b86359efca3b8a893deffcf4e45113d","tid":694626,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2da374f378007c8a9311471c19e8387ab79d874e","tid":694626,"uid":18279,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"而今年的情況與2016年較為接近，美斯國內雙冠，c朗獲歐聯，而以過往經驗金球多陪隨歐聯，所以c朗機會遠高於美斯。<br />\n<br />\n但2016年c朗在國家隊獲歐國盃，而美斯則在百年美洲盃失利。故今年關鍵在於世界杯。<br />\n<br />\n估計:<br />\n<br />\n若美斯獲世界杯，必奪金球。<br />\n<br />\n若美斯比C朗走得更遠，到決賽，金球機率五五分。<br />\n<br />\n若美斯比C朗走得更遠，不到決賽，金球機率低。<br />\n<br />\n其他情況C朗必奪金球。"},{"pid":"aaa0790f3602671ceb5d6fdb2cea3ca00e5105a7","tid":694626,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbcbdedb8b86359efca3b8a893deffcf4e45113d","tid":694626,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"無錯美斯的確處於劣勢"},{"pid":"93e8d986fe604d53b78ffeaf026b87b0c82afbd3","tid":694626,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4401b3f676567adfa22a9a40be39a1dc4c7f234f","tid":694626,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"93e8d986fe604d53b78ffeaf026b87b0c82afbd3","tid":694626,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa0790f3602671ceb5d6fdb2cea3ca00e5105a7","tid":694626,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbcbdedb8b86359efca3b8a893deffcf4e45113d","tid":694626,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"無錯美斯的確處於劣勢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"助攻多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過金球睇團隊多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f21907d7d4368ba1917d7c8d21b180b06f475e","tid":694626,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"睇樓主咁講其實金球獎都算公平<br />\n<br />\n主要睇球隊成續<br />\n唔睇個人數據"},{"pid":"aa9d6d525655428f16613fa406746d39c5bdef91","tid":694626,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:37:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bbdf5d59260a1a04c083d743c760362145f58a2","tid":694626,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15f21907d7d4368ba1917d7c8d21b180b06f475e","tid":694626,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"睇樓主咁講其實金球獎都算公平<br />\n<b